Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.02,0:00:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,3004)}So Ra No Wo To
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, my little chickens?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to advance! Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are our allies?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forty degrees, left.\NPrepare to fire main cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:01:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Range 400!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Load shell. Type: heat round!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Origa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been locked in this thing for three days.\NI'm not dying till we can take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Main gun aimed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna, report to the rear:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.32,0:02:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"One tank destroyed.\NContinue the advance!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia, back her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's flashing.\NBut it isn't lightning, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Three o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,3000)\i1}Kamiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(1,3000)}Higoya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chirping Crickets -\NSpirits Down the River
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Noël! Put your back into it,\Nor they won't get clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold in the winter, but I love how\Ncool this building is in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Aren't Filicia and Rio-sempai\Non cleaning duty today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they were busy,\Nand asked us to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Filicia-san's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she wasn't hungry,\Nso we could eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you preparing dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be written up for\Nplaying with the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for Obon, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's Obon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fiesta des Lumières.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fiesta des Lumières is a holiday\Nunique to southern Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It originated from a folk religion\Nthat believed that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for a specific period of time during the summer,\Nthe dead return to the world of the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Floating paper lanterns down\Nthe river sends them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In some places, this festival is called Obon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? So it's the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits returning...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean we'll see ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paper lanterns... How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We used to make fires and\Nstuff back home, but-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.93,0:06:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dead go to Heaven\Nand stay there forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only bad things are stuck\Nwandering the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in church...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and give us a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, when did you go shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They looked tasty,\Nso we bought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will this do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom and dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Even the church is in on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Fie-thingy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Central Orthodox Church\Nwould be up in arms over it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we're in the middle\Nof nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not very serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my town,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we would make horses and cows
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,out of cucumbers and eggplants\Nfor our ancestors to ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we all danced to\Nmake them happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to make some, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Last year, we just watched, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's part of our job to maintain\Ngood relations with the locals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't really think about it,\Nit's just a nice little festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Filicia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.87,0:09:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just screwed up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't make mistakes\Nlike that often.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.95,0:09:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how hot it's been\Nthese last few days...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't really been\Nable to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's acting kind of strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't eat her lunch, and she\Nblew off work to buy watermelons...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got a lot on her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll go talk to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some things she\Ndoesn't want anyone to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about it, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I read the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know about it first-hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it steady. Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, there's a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there was a monster\Nthat looked just like the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe there used to be\Nall kinds of living things in this sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ever hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the world is slowly ending,\Nand someday there will be no humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a rumor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it's true, then what\Nare we fighting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideograms?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I were able to read\Nyour last words...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,2100)}Is it from the old era?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Origa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Martina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the only one left...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still survivors\Nin this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just the last remnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A few remaining bubbles on\Nthe surface of the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world can never regain\Nthe glory it once had.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to decide that for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So end it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be far too painful, living a miserable\Nlife in a world filled with despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there some meaning to survival\Nin a world like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my squad had only arrived half a day earlier,\Nthis never would have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, Princess Iria...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last year, you ignored the\NFiesta des Lumières.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty colors, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's made in Treize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought it at the last market.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. They used to\Nbe everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to protect the country,\Nthe people, like they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if they've really come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted them to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. I may have\Nmade them worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I failed as a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, don't try and carry\Nit all on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the least, even I can listen to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll honor that and tell you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotten fatter this summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't start losing weight, I won't be\Nable to fit into my winter clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that if you only eat watermelon,\Nyou'll lose weight,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I'd try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened at\Nthe Vingt front...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Did you think I was\Nremembering that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You weren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you made one, too,\NKureha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't believe in\Nsouls and stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Who are you sending, Filicia-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My old friends
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a soldier whose\Nname I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people who made me realize\Nsomething important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could those people be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if something's bothering\Nyou or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not be able to help... But!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I worried you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to worry for you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:20:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always do things to\Nmake you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to worry about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you too, Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay as you are. Won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you're always teaching me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to not fear putting your\Nfeelings into words...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia... Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back next year, ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad... Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother... Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.59,0:21:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rio. You were asking if there\Nwas some meaning in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.25,0:21:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was the only one who survived,\Nit was all I could think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why had I, alone, survived?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I realized,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:22:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there's no meaning\Nin this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you can\Nfind your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've found mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.57,0:22:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The meaning to my being here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then the priest...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.42,0:22:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.71,0:22:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he was super selfish,\Nso Yumina-neechan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.09,0:22:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.63,0:22:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want them to\Nsuffer like I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Phone Duty - We Have an Emergency
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.75,0:24:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.71,0:24:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phone Duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.40,0:24:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Have an Emergency!
